{"tid":2068886,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（暴動了）蘋果浦東店遭一男子破壞　多部Mac電腦被砸毀在地","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:20:18.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8304a6a009ad7dbf9811c5b8ce7929a17140fd","tid":2068886,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"2020-06-17 12:30<br />\n<br />\n位於上海浦東新區陸家嘴國金中心的Apple Store浦東店，是上海首間、內地第2間蘋果零售店，周二（16日）遭到一名29歲男子入店破壞。該店多部Mac電腦被肢解、砸毀在地，現場「屍橫遍野」，場面相當混亂。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場後將男子控制，在詢問後發現其男子「語無倫次，邏輯混亂，無法正常交流」，隨後將其帶至派出所作進一步調查。該店亦即刻暫停營業，至今日（17日）重開。"},{"pid":"0c972587091b090ed15ad55254ed5f831c37adaa","tid":2068886,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"報國恥都要拉 叫人點愛國呀"},{"pid":"40566d10a417c8e94618ec1c0db3f308b075baee","tid":2068886,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c972587091b090ed15ad55254ed5f831c37adaa","tid":2068886,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"報國恥都要拉 叫人點愛國呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"唔通會同你講拉完放走左?"},{"pid":"1a7ca4465d983230a71800e3f29769f361944b1e","tid":2068886,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"山寨定正版apple shop 先？"},{"pid":"437399a73c475126d7b50addafc4605848909913","tid":2068886,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:14:21.000Z","msg":"幫美資裝修<br />\n<br />\n愛國無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574699e4ed4d95226c4dd1d5e3859759d7bb2b47","tid":2068886,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"支持! 繼續喺微博煽動先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好搞多次好似當年反日示威嘅規模咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxdLie7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2